message.body: I'm going to grab the van this morning. Is it relatively organized or does it need a clean out?
Van is chaos. I was planning on spending a few hrs organizing it
Ok. I want to park it on my street and finish getting the graffiti off. Are you able to organize it today?

Is it ok to pay you Monday for this week? I am waiting for panama check to clear and the money from 309 is coming from penn so I doubt I'll have it anytime soon and still waiting on Mary-knight money.
Thanks. What is the van plan?
I'm sleeping now. I'll do it later today
I didn't clean out the van bc it was raining all day. I will take my stuff out so u can use it and I can come clean it out when it's not raining
